					you're skilled not only at talking to witnesses without revealing _
					the truth, but at figuring out what they really saw, even if they _
					don't realize it. When necessary, you are unequaled at stealth _
					and concealment. In a hostile situation, you use the latter to _
					your advantage - while the rest of the team is charging at the _
